# webOS TV knowledge (mandatory)

When working under `client/`, use MCP **`search_knowledge_base`** with
`collection="webos-tv"` before implementing or changing webOS-specific behavior.

## Required

1. Nest memory workflow if the nest checkout is available (project + context memory).
2. **`search_knowledge_base(query="...", collection="webos-tv")`** — platform APIs,
   `appinfo.json`, events, Developer Mode, packaging.

Hooks in the nest repo enforce this when paths include `client/`.

## Index refresh (nest repo)

```bash
cd /path/to/nest && ./scripts/fetch-webos-knowledge.sh
```

